These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, gardening, card-games, photography
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, marigold, orchid
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsorchid is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | fanta    | tea      | iced-tea      | soy-milk    |
| Hobby   | photography | cooking | gardening | card-games |
| Flower     | tulip    | orchid       | marigold     | begonia     |

