.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
House: tower, farmhouse, modern, victorian
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, fuchsia, orange, white
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, august, september, april
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1
2. the tower house is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the modern house is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| House          | tower     | victorian     | farmhouse       | modern    |
| Color         | fuchsia | orange   | red | white |
| Birthday   | april    | september | august    | november        |

