.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, ritmeester, bolivar, tiparillo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, january, march
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, fisherman, software-developer, manager
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
3. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the manager##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the electrician##1
7. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
8. the software-developer is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar      | bluemaster | ritmeester  | bolivar    | tiparillo |
| Birthday   | january   | march  | november  | july    |
| Job         | fisherman    | manager | electrician | software-developer  |

