.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, lavender, blood-red, brown
There are 4 different nationalities: german, japanese, italian, thai
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, engineer, freelancer, firefighter
1. the engineer is between the japanese and the person who likes orange##2
2. the german is on the left or right of the japanese##3
3. the freelancer is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1
5. the scientist is the person who likes brown##1
6. the japanese is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the person who likes brown is on the right of the german##1
8. the thai is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Color          | blood-red   | orange     | lavender | brown |
| Nationality   | italian | thai | german   | japanese     |
| Job           | firefighter | freelancer      | engineer     | scientist       |

