.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, disco, soul, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, video-games, sudoku, photography
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower, iris, daffodil
1. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the fan of soul and the fan of disco##2
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the fan of funk##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
8. the fan of soul is the person who growsiris##1
9. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre          | soul      | funk | disco      | d&b |
| Hobby           | video-games | cooking | photography | sudoku   |
| Flower   | iris    | daffodil   | bellflower     | balloon-flower   |

