.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
House: modern, ranch-style, wooden, tower
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, lizard, pony
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, baking, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the modern house##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the pony##1
3. the modern house is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
6. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
8. the ranch-style house is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| House           | modern    | ranch-style   | wooden | tower |
| Pet   | fish     | lizard   | pony         | ferret        |
| Hobby         | writing | filmmaking | baking         | collecting       |

