3. the coach is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
4. the software-developer is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the coach##1
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
