5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the brazilian is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

