4. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
7. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person driving the car##1
8. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Pet          | frog   | goldfish | rat | hamster |
| Flower   | iris   | azalea     | daffodil      | amaryllis  |
| Transport   | scooter | motorbike   | car    | boat   |

