3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
6. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the art-deco house##2
7. the townhouse house is the person traveling to hannover##1
8. the cottage house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
