5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who likes chestnut and the person who likes turquise##2
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
7. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
